title: National Socialist Ultimate Starter Pack
description:
BROUGHT TO YOU BY BEN GARRISON

A collection of essential works for the aspiring Stormtrooper. 

Included in this collection:


Triumph of the Will
The Eternal Jew
Adolf Hitler - The Greatest Story Never Told
Hitler's War - What Historians Neglect to Mention
The Epic Story of the Waffen-SS
One Third of the Holocaust
Spielberg's Hoax - The Last Days of the Big Lie
The Majdanek Gas Chamber Myth
"Der Untergang (Downfall)"

A massive collection of e-books, including the works of Goebbels, Goring, Heydrich, Rosenberg, Joyce, Pound, Lindbergh, Pierce, Jordan, Koehl, Rockwell, Mosley, Yockey, Codreanu, Devi, Serrano, Irving, Hoggan, Bacque, Degrelle, Rommel, Ford, Wagner, Schramm, Toaff, MacDonald, and many more. You also get the full battery of Revisionist work, from Mattogno, Graf, Rudolf, Piper, Rassinier, Walsh, Yeager, and others. 

Also included is a choice selection of music, from the archives of Zyklon Ben himself.

And this is all just a taste of the happy surprises that await you
